             was indicted for <rs id="t18330704-118-off602" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18330704-118-off602" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18330704-118-off602" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18330704-118-cd603" type="crimeDate">24th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330704-118-off602 t18330704-118-cd603"></join>, 43lbs., of lead, value 5s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18330704-118-victim1194" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Little
                  <interp inst="t18330704-118-victim1194" type="surname" value="Little"></interp>
